ity of further exploitation of related\nmolecular intercalations in this and other systems in order to greatly optimize\nthe superconducting properties in this family.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Mar 2012 17:22:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Mar 2012 14:09:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
